<div id="articles">

<div class="article" id="art1">
<span class="sd-info-block" style="display: none">
	<span class="sd-key-sid">08/09/21/160222</span>
	<span class="type">story</span>
	
</span>



<div class="generaltitle" >
	<div class="title">
		<h3 >
			Palin Email Hacker Found
			
		</h3>
	</div>
</div>
	<div class="details"><small>

	
	Posted by
	
	<a href="mailto:soulskillatslashdotdotorg">Soulskill</a>

	on Sun Sep 21, 2008 12:01 PM<br>
	from the do-not-pass-go dept.
	</small></div>
	<div class="body">
		<div class="topic">
		
		
		
			<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/search.pl?tid=61">
				<img src="//a.fsdn.com/sd/topics/topicgovt.gif" width="57" height="80" alt="Government" title="Government" >
			</a>
		
		
			
			
			
			
				
					<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/search.pl?tid=83" class="topic2">
						<img src="//a.fsdn.com/sd/topics/topicprivacy.gif" width="71" height="53" alt="Privacy" title="Privacy" >
					</a>
				
		
			
			
			
				
					<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/search.pl?tid=76" class="topic2">
						<img src="//a.fsdn.com/sd/topics/topicsecurity.gif" width="59" height="78" alt="Security" title="Security" >
					</a>
				
		
			
			
			
				
					<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/search.pl?tid=209" class="topic2">
						<img src="//a.fsdn.com/sd/topics/topicus.gif" width="80" height="61" alt="United States" title="United States" >
					</a>
				
		
			
			
			
				
					<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/search.pl?tid=96" class="topic2">
						<img src="//a.fsdn.com/sd/topics/topicpolitics.gif" width="61" height="43" alt="Politics" title="Politics" >
					</a>
				
		
			
			
			
				
		
		
		</div>
		<div class="intro">
			mortonda writes to tell us that the person responsible for <a href="http://www.tgdaily.com/html_tmp/content-view-39405-108.html">breaching Sarah Palin's private email account</a> has been found. We <a href="//news.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=08/09/17/1949222&amp;tid=158">discussed the breach</a> last Wednesday, shortly before the hacker, a University of Tennessee-Knoxville student, <a href="http://blog.wired.com/27bstroke6/2008/09/palin-e-mail-ha.html">posted a message detailing his methods</a>.  Wired has a story examining the <a href="http://blog.wired.com/27bstroke6/2008/09/palin-hack-migh.html">potential legal consequences</a> for the hacker.
		</div>





		







	</div>
	<div class="tags"><span id="updown-" class="vote">
	<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/faq/UI.shtml#ui700" onclick="return false" class="up" title="Vote this item up">+</a>
	<a href="//politics.slashdot.org/faq/UI.shtml#ui700" onclick="return false" class="down" title="Vote this item down">-</a>
</span></div>

